FAQ

What is an AI design?

An AI design is a design created by artificial intelligence (AI) technology. AI can be used to quickly generate high-quality images, videos and text, and even for building complete websites in record time. Wix offers a variety of AI tools to help you build and grow your business.

What types of content can I design with AI?

There are many different types of content you can design with AI. Wix sites come with a suite of AI design tools that can help you create or enhance many aspects of your site individually including:


  • Text: Generate compelling written content for titles, blog posts, about us pages, product descriptions and more.

  • Images: Design unique, high-quality images for your site in seconds that match your brand's look and feel. Or, use AI to customize existing images by removing elements, replacing components or improving their resolution.

  • Site sections: Use AI to instantly add new sections to your site complete with design, content and images that match your site's look and feel.

  • Section layouts: View different layout suggestions and see how they’d look with your content. 

Are Wix’s AI tools free to use?

With Wix, you have access to a suite of free AI tools that can help you build and customize websites, as well as scale and manage your business. With an upgraded Wix package, you’ll get access to even more advanced AI tools.

Who owns the copyright of AI-generated designs?

AI-generated designs created with Wix have no copyright license or restrictions. You are free to use them wherever you would like.

Is there a limit to the number of AI designs I can create?

No, there is no limit to the number of AI designs you can create using Wix's tools. You have the freedom to generate unlimited websites, images and text content. You can also explore various design options and refine any specific piece of AI-created content as much as you’d like until you are happy with the results.

Are AI tools easy to use for people with no technical background?

Absolutely. Wix’s AI tools are intuitive and straightforward to use regardless of your technical background or skills.

What additional AI tools does Wix offer?

In addition to the AI-powered tools highlighted on this page, Wix also offers many additional tools to help you create your brand and grow your online presence, including:


  • AI Logo Maker: Create a unique logo in minutes with AI-generated images, brand names and taglines.

  • AI Business Name Generator: Get hundreds of company name ideas in seconds.

  • App Builder: Make your own fully branded mobile app that showcases your professionalism and sets your business apart.

  • AI alt text for portfolio images: Quickly create optimized alt text for your portfolio images with AI-generated text.

  • App recommendations: Get AI-curated suggestions of helpful apps for your site on the Wix App Market.

  • AI text for templates: When you create your site from a template, get AI-written content for every part of your site written in a unified brand voice and optimized to fit each site section.
